author: Warner Todd Huston
title: Fake News: Wash Post Changes Story on Trump ‘Firing’ D.C. Nat’l Guard General

organizations.name: d.c. nat’l guard general  the washington post

text: The Washington Post wrote on Friday that President-elect Donald J. Trump "fired" the commanding General of the D.C. National Guard who is heading up the military presence during the coming inaugural event — in the middle of the oath of office ceremony. Yet a second story on Saturday did not contain the claim.
